The paper discusses a system for fast and quality-guaranteed machine learning training, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of probabilistic principal component analysis (PPCA), which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of large datasets and the need for efficient computation suggests that the paper could also be categorized under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of generalized linear models, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and statistics (cs.ST).
